{"tid":1743421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仲對1124投票有疑問既入一入黎","createTime":"2019-11-21T07:45:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T22:35:47.000Z","uid":206482,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd1d868dc9fe472bd4e4b2e1e160331a00c5efc3","tid":1743421,"uid":206482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"你地可能覺得制度已經崩壞<br />\n投黎都無意思<br />\n或者可能覺得 建制一定贏硬 唔洗諗<br />\n<br />\n你地呢個諗法就錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先，我諗有出過去遊行甚至前線既<br />\n都會好清楚個種無力感，好想去推反個政府<br />\n每日睇電視見到高官既嘴臉，就好想打爆部電視<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信我 我同你一樣， 但係<br />\n以家一個咁好激到佢地札札跳既機會<br />\n點解要放過？你諗下老鼠芬見到區選建制大敗既時候佢個樣<br />\n再諗下林鄭平時個死老豆樣，再見到咁既選情<br />\n個樣由死老豆變死埋老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗起到開心啦 係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再推一步說，自己人當選，代表渣正牌拎政府錢去買豬嘴<br />\n以家政府比錢你去推反佢自己 有幾何咁既機會阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之，到時投自己人，百利以無一害，最重要既係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投完一定要話自己投左建制，等佢估計唔到選情</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"1882d11e09e1f266c028177183aceac5243a440c","tid":1743421,"uid":206482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:46:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"933ebcbcbc5e8af6e78d31856006ed976b467f73","tid":1743421,"uid":206482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:46:46.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"6b3d32330b4b63f04c726dda85a80e56f2944524","tid":1743421,"uid":206482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:47:00.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"0a21196758eb8fe04bc69ca433654f5